@node Main "CheckItOut! V01.02c Help"

(c) Copyright 1994,1995 Bug Free Development

CheckItOut!  is  a  powerful  personal  finance management tool used for 
tracking  your  assets and liabilities. You can configure the program to 
manage  and  balance  single checking account or many accounts including 
checking, savings, credit cards, cash, other liabilities and assets.

