@node MenuReportsSummaryByCategory "CheckItOut!: Menu/ Reports/ Summary By Category"

When  you  select  the  @{b}Summary by Category@{ub} report, the @{"Find Transaction" link FindTransactions } 
form  is  displayed.  Filling in fields in the displayed query form will 
limit which transactions are included in the report.

The  Summary  by  Category  report is similar to the Itemize by Category 
report  except  that  the  detailed list of all the transactions are not 
included.  Only  the  category  totals for the transactions that met the 
search  criteria  you  entered  in  the  find  transaction query form are 
displayed.   There   are   totals   for   each   category  that contains 
subcategories   and   totals   for   income,   expenses,  transfers, and 
categories  that  have  no type specified. There is a grand total at the 
end of the report.

Use  the  arrow keys or scroll bars to move around in the report window. 
You  can  use  @{"<Right-Amiga-P>" link MenuProgramPrint }  to output the report to the printer or a 
file.

