@node Support "CheckItOut!: Support"

Support  for  the  CheckItOut!  Program is available through CompuServe, 
the Internet, and US Mail.

For  the  purposes of supporting the CheckItOut! program, communications 
via  CompuServe  and  Internet  Mail  are  encouraged. Should there be a 
need   to   communicate  with  me  (Jim)  or  Bug  Free  Development via 
telephone,  please  send mail to me at @{"Bug Free Development" link BugFreeDev } stating your 
phone  number,  the  nature, and need to speak voice. If it is felt that 
a telephone conversation is warranted I will call you.

@endnode

@node BugFreeDev "CheckItOut!: Bug Free Development"

Bug  Free  Development  is  a New Hampshire Business. It was formed as a 
means  of  marketing  and  supporting  the CheckItOut! program and other 
computer related business interests.

The US Mail address for Bug Free Development is ...

                  Bug Free Development
                  P.O. Box 7042
                  Nashua, NH  03060

The CompuServe Mail address for Bug Free Development is ...

                  71171,3015

The Internet Mail address for Bug Free Development is ...

                  71171.3015@CompuServe.com

Correspondence should be addressed to Jim.

@endnode

